1.5.3.name: wordpress/cart66-cloud
1.5.3.description:
Cart66 Cloud let's you sell anything and handles all the details of keeping your store secure. Sell digital files, ship products, and even sell memberships and subscriptions. Cart66 Cloud includes a built-in recurring billing engine and support for 50 payment gateways. Membership management features to restrict access to content on your site is included too! Unlike other e-commerce plugins where you have to buy add-ons and worry about SSL certificates and security scans, Cart66 Cloud gives you everything you need all in one easy to use package. We even handle all of the requirements for PCI compliance for you so you don't have to do anything but start selling.

Features

Cart66 Cloud is the most secure way to sell with WordPress and provides a full set of e-commerce features including:
